            <note xml:id="foot.f2">The eldest child was <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_9292.xml">Henry Augustus Dupré</ref>; the twins were <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_9293.xml">Percy Vivian Dupré</ref> and <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_9294.xml">Frederick Harold Dupré</ref>.</note>
           
            
